Package com.trefis.partitioner

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Partitioner<T,C>
    Partitioner that partitions things based on type and by criteria
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDoublePartitioner
    Using Doubles this partitioner implements many of the helper methods that are needed for doing any basic partitioning on Doubles.
    GreedyDoublePartionerTest  
    GreedyDoublePartitioner
    This is a partitioner that has been implemented with a basic greedy algorithm.
    OneToOneDoublePartioner
    Partitions the data to ensure that only one value will be in a group by itself.
    OneToOneDoublePartionerTest
    Tests to ensure that the partitioner works as expected
    RandomDoublePartioner
    This is a partitioner that has been implemented that randomly tries assign the values.
    RandomDoublePartionerTest
    Tests a the randomness of the random partitioner test
    SortedGreedyDoublePartitioner
    This is a partitioner that has been implemented with a greedy algorithm but sorts the data before it does the partitioning The default sort is ascending.
